articles.title: Europe's Vega rocket aces its final mission (video) - Space.com
articles.description: Vega lifted off at 9:50 p.m. ET tonight (Sept. 4), carrying the Sentinel-2C Earth-observing satellite skyward.
articles.content:
Europe's Vega rocket aced its final mission tonight (Sept. 4).
